jobs.title: UX Designer
description: Develop, test, and maintain responsive, high-performance web applications.
Collaborate with UI/UX designers to translate wireframes into code.
Integrate front-end components with APIs and backend services.
Write clean, maintainable code following best practices.
Collaborate in Agile/Scrum ceremonies and sprint reviews.

jobs.title: Frontend Developer
description: Implement reusable UI components using React and Tailwind CSS.
Work closely with backend teams to ensure smooth integration.
Focus on performance, accessibility, and code scalability.

jobs.title: Data Analyst
description: Analyze product data to provide insights for the content team.
Create dashboards and visualizations using Tableau and Python.
Collaborate with engineers and designers to inform product decisions.

jobs.title: Data Scientist
description: Data cleaning and preparation: Collect, clean, and preprocess large datasets to ensure accuracy and readiness for analysis.
Data analysis: Conduct exploratory data analysis to identify patterns, trends, and insights within the data.

jobs.title: Data Scientist
description: Data analysis: Conduct exploratory data analysis to identify patterns, trends, and insights within the data.
